2026-03-16T22:27:58-04:00 | attempt-3 | area=evaluation | hypothesis=Even after fixing the benchmark cell, it still points at a fixture copy of the skill, so edits in `skills/skill-arena-compare/SKILL.md` would never reach the benchmark. Point the local-path source at `skills/skill-arena-compare` directly. | classification=false-negative | result=KEPT | before=0/40 pass | after=0/40 pass | reason=Pass rate stayed flat, but the new run materialized the root `skills/skill-arena-compare` directory inside the benchmark workspace, so future skill edits now affect the measured `skill` column.
